name: NewLife CPR
tag_list: cpr, first-aid, aed, certification, training, courses, classes, bloodborne, pathogens
overview: NewLife CPR provides the modern online training solution for the traditional classroom setting for CPR, First Aid and AED certification and training classes. They provide the most up to date curriculim for both layperson rescuers and Professional Healthcare Providers. With their comprehensive online courses, you can become certified in any of their online CPR courses in the comfort of your own home. You can work at your own pace, pause your course, leave the course and return anytime you like. You can also return at any time for a refresher, and you may return as many times as you like until you are confident in your abilities. This is an excellent resource for quality CPR AED and First Aid training and certification.
